{
  "ALBUM": { ... },
  "DUMMY_PHOTOS": [ ... ],
  "NEW_POST": { ... }
}

--------------------------------------------------

ALBUM RULES

Fields:

country → Chinese country name  
countryCode → ISO country code  
region → region or city name  
city → must be exactly the same as region  

